gameplay

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • gameplay.Player

  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents the players participating in the game, including the pieces they hold as well as their hands. It is important to note that a player's color uniquely identifies the player.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Team 10 - SOEN6441
